          "type": "assistant",
          "text": "## Design Section 4: Project Management\n\n**Concept**: Projects are top-level organizational units. Every chat belongs to a project. The project's working directory sets the agent's file operation context.\n\n**Data Model**:\n```python\n@dataclass\nclass Project:\n    id: str              # UUID\n    name: str            # Display name (editable)\n    path: Path           # Absolute path to project root\n    created_at: datetime\n    updated_at: datetime\n    is_active: bool      # Soft delete support\n\n@dataclass  \nclass ChatSession:\n    id: str\n    project_id: str      # Foreign key to project\n    title: str\n    created_at: datetime\n    updated_at: datetime\n```\n\n**User Flow**:\n\n1. **First Launch**: User sees empty project list with \"Add Your First Project\" CTA\n2. **Add Project**: \n   - Modal opens with path input\n   - User enters absolute path (e.g., `/home/user/my-project`)\n   - System validates path exists and is allowed by `DEEPAGENTS_ALLOWED_DIRS`\n   - Project name defaults to directory name (editable)\n3. **Project View**: Shows all chats for selected project + \"New Chat\" button\n4. **Switch Projects**: Sidebar shows project list, click to switch\n\n**UI Layout with Projects**:\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ ▓▓▓ AGENT-TUI WEB ▓▓▓        [+ Add Project] [⚙️]          │  \n├──────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ ▓ PROJECTS ▓ │  ▓▓▓ MY-PROJECT ▓▓▓  [+ New Chat]           │\n│ ──────────── │                                              │\n│ ⏵ proj-one   │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│   proj-two   │  │ Chat messages here...                  │  │\n│   proj-three │  └────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│ ──────────── │                                              │\n│ [+ Add New]  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│              │  │ > Type message...              [Send]  │  │\n└──────────────┴──┴──────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Adding a Project** (Neobrutalist Modal):\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────┐\n│ ▓▓▓ ADD NEW PROJECT ▓▓▓    [X] │\n├─────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                 │\n│  Project Path:                  │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ /home/user/projects/    │    │\n│  │ my-awesome-app          │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────┘    │\n│  [Browse]                       │\n│                                 │\n│  Display Name:                  │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ my-awesome-app          │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────┘    │\n│                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ ✅ Path validated       │    │\n│  │ 📁 12 files detected    │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────┘    │\n│                                 │\n│     [Cancel]  [Add Project]     │\n│                                 │\n└─────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Security Integration**:\n- Path validation against `DEEPAGENTS_ALLOWED_DIRS` before adding\n- Clear error if path not allowed: \"This path is outside your allowed directories. Add it to DEEPAGENTS_ALLOWED_DIRS to use it.\"\n- Project path stored in database, validated on every file operation\n\n**Database Schema** (SQLite):\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE projects (\n    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    path TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,\n    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT 1\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE chat_sessions (\n    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n    project_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n    title TEXT,\n    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(id)\n);\n\nCREATE INDEX idx_chats_project ON chat_sessions(project_id);\n```\n\n**API Endpoints**:\n```python\n# Projects\nGET    /api/projects              # List all projects\nPOST   /api/projects              # Create new project\nGET    /api/projects/{id}         # Get project details\nPATCH  /api/projects/{id}         # Update project name\nDELETE /api/projects/{id}         # Soft delete project\n\n# Chats (project-scoped)\nGET    /api/projects/{id}/chats   # List chats for project\nPOST   /api/projects/{id}/chats   # Create new chat in project\n```\n\n**Session Sharing with TUI**:\n- TUI uses existing `sessions.py` (flat chat list)\n- Web adds project layer on top\n- When TUI creates a chat, it's \"unassociated\" (no project)\n- Web shows unassociated chats in an \"Other\" section or hides them\n- Migration path: web user can \"claim\" unassociated chats into a project\n\n**Does this project management approach work for you?**",
